{"tid":2354821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚德塞: 對中國官員未確認容許世衛專家組入境 感到非常失望","createTime":"2021-01-05T18:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T13:32:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":174,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"e454b6fa90e58d031966f64ae4436c781ab8cfab","tid":2354821,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/148160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F148160&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=c8ba0a5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/148160</a><br />\n<br />\n世衛總幹事譚德塞表示，他對中國官員至今仍未最終確認容許世衛專家組入境，以調查新型冠狀病毒的起源，感到非常失望。譚德塞在世衛例行記者會上，罕有地批評北京當局，指根據世衛與中國政府之間安排的一部分，國際科學團隊的成員過去24小時內，已經陸續啟程前往中國，但他了解到，中方官員仍未最終確認專家組需要取得的必要許可，部分成員無法起行。譚德塞表示，世衛與中方高層保持聯繫，他清楚表明有關調查是世衛的優先事項，並已經確保中方加快內部程序，期望專家組可以盡快執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n2021-01-06 02:04:24"},{"pid":"9803a3525f2320a2d6d917bdfe537671419e0e66","tid":2354821,"uid":126919,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618dd3a9b6f749b68b0337cab8ace38f9af1940a","tid":2354821,"uid":173271,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"自己人使乜查<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16161bf4025c46875237961e870b6551eabb117b","tid":2354821,"uid":129169,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:25:39.000Z","msg":"condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi